(1500mg/100ml) Ingredients: Water, Guarana extract 12.5%,Natural Flavour, Citric Acid The SuddenRush Guarana Natural Energy Shot/Strong is a liquid energizer, with a high dose of Guarana combined with vanilla flavour. One shot contains 165mg pure and natural Guarana-Coffeine. This shot provides extra energy to the body and gives it an additonal 4-6 hour energy push to maximize your daily performance at work, during exams or at sports. Best used half an hour before sport excercises or challenges, presentations, exams, important meetings, or simply after a big meal. 33kcal per shot. Available at Pharmacies and Drugstores
